  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trapped in your routine, the days become increasingly strange as your mind begins to fail.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512810/extras/cf26cc6dafeb155069901fc5ee43c38a.poster.avif?t=1743708451\" width=720 height=486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512810/extras/cf26cc6dafeb155069901fc5ee43c38a.webm?t=1743708451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512810/extras/cf26cc6dafeb155069901fc5ee43c38a.mp4?t=1743708451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fractured Perception is an atmospheric first-person horror game where you'll live your routine while experiencing weird events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a short story where you'll feel your mental state being torn apart as you learn more about this mystery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512810/extras/9201ac80a186251bf315b161ba192fd2.poster.avif?t=1743708451\" width=720 height=486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512810/extras/9201ac80a186251bf315b161ba192fd2.webm?t=1743708451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512810/extras/9201ac80a186251bf315b161ba192fd2.mp4?t=1743708451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll solve puzzles to unravel this story.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Walking simulator</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512810/extras/bca806589d5639d354ada04e0711593b.poster.avif?t=1743708451\" width=720 height=486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512810/extras/bca806589d5639d354ada04e0711593b.webm?t=1743708451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512810/extras/bca806589d5639d354ada04e0711593b.mp4?t=1743708451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trapped in your routine, the days become increasingly strange as your mind begins to fail.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512810/extras/cf26cc6dafeb155069901fc5ee43c38a.poster.avif?t=1743708451\" width=720 height=486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512810/extras/cf26cc6dafeb155069901fc5ee43c38a.webm?t=1743708451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512810/extras/cf26cc6dafeb155069901fc5ee43c38a.mp4?t=1743708451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fractured Perception is an atmospheric first-person horror game where you'll live your routine while experiencing weird events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a short story where you'll feel your mental state being torn apart as you learn more about this mystery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512810/extras/9201ac80a186251bf315b161ba192fd2.poster.avif?t=1743708451\" width=720 height=486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512810/extras/9201ac80a186251bf315b161ba192fd2.webm?t=1743708451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512810/extras/9201ac80a186251bf315b161ba192fd2.mp4?t=1743708451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll solve puzzles to unravel this story.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Walking simulator</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragrap